<collectionCode box="[1380,1398,1421,1442]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">R</collectionCode>
<subScript attach="left" box="[1398,1406,1430,1442]" fontSize="5" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">2</subScript>
of forewing most often fused and forked with 
<collectionCode box="[1333,1351,1451,1472]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">R</collectionCode>
<subScript attach="left" box="[1350,1358,1461,1473]" fontSize="5" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">3</subScript>
, sometimes separate; 
<collectionCode box="[1025,1043,1482,1503]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">R</collectionCode>
<subScript attach="left" box="[1043,1051,1491,1503]" fontSize="5" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">3</subScript>
or 
<collectionCode box="[1105,1123,1482,1503]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">R</collectionCode>
<subScript attach="left" box="[1123,1147,1491,1504]" fontSize="5" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">2+3</subScript>
of forewing most often separate from 
<collectionCode box="[1001,1019,1512,1533]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">R</collectionCode>
<subScript attach="left" box="[1019,1027,1522,1534]" fontSize="5" pageId="36" pageNumber="258">4</subScript>
